[SN]TITLE[SN]
Trump would not turn down presidency if he won - son

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Donald Trump’s son Eric has flatly denied suggestions his father may not take up the presidency if he wins the election in November.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
20 July 2016 Last updated at 19:19 BST
He was speaking to BBC Newsnight’s Emily Maitlis after speculation on the issue in the US media.
He said there was “no question” Donald Trump would take up the position. "You don't do this for fun," he said.
